        " عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «ضَمِنْتُ لِمَنْ زَارَ قَبْرَ أَبِي بِطُوسَ عَارِفاً بِحَقِّهِ اَلْجَنَّةَ عَلَى اَللَّهِ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3186 - Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Jawad (as) said:\n\"I guarantee Paradise with Allah (swt), the Mighty and Exalted, for whoever visits the grave of my father in Tus, recognizing his right.\""
        ]
